{"tid":597146,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"江蘇夫婦網上自學開鎖　瘋狂爆竊40多次卻偷廢紙","createTime":"2018-03-18T10:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T12:14:25.000Z","uid":3393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"28a6fd941ae9fb107532ede5987d4cf4283210a8","tid":597146,"uid":3393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180318/photo/bkncn-20180318162749358-0318_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180318164411\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180318%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180318162749358-0318_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180318164411&h=b6599bee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180318/photo/bkncn-20180318162749358-0318_05011_001_02p.jpg?20180318164411\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180318%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180318162749358-0318_05011_001_02p.jpg%3F20180318164411&h=ee4732c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n江蘇鎮江市京口區一對26歲夫婦平日無所事事，在網上自學開鎖技術後，從去年12月到今年1月期間，瘋狂入屋爆竊40多次，平均每天犯案1次。案件引起警方重視，經翻查現場閉路電視畫面，警方終在上周日（10日）抓獲該對分別王姓及陳姓的男女。<br />\n<br />\n經查，王男及陳女結婚剛剛一年，平日好吃懶做又無一技之長，便在網上自學開鎖技術，並購買開鎖工具連環爆竊。為了滿足爆竊慾望及逃避追查，兩人犯案後期更開始自製犯案工具，入屋爆竊主要以現金和貴金屬為主。不過，兩人亦有「走漏眼」時候，曾誤把一大堆糧票當成文物，偷走並帶到文物市場出售時，才知已是「廢紙」。<br />\n<br />\n目前，這對小夫妻二人因涉嫌盜竊，已被警方刑事拘留，案件仍在調查當中。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180318/bkncn-20180318162749358-0318_05011_001.html?refer=hn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180318%2Fbkncn-20180318162749358-0318_05011_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn&d=dFmqmi4XpSM0kiMQxQkSqU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=8da87e45\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180318/bkncn-20180318162749358-0318_05011_001.html?refer=hn</a>"},{"pid":"21fde9681c66aa876672309473cba4240e8674e4","tid":597146,"uid":27568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:09:21.000Z","msg":"自我增值<br />\n自學成材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b7385c5ad137495b5e72c1f96a8eb920c4aa18","tid":597146,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21fde9681c66aa876672309473cba4240e8674e4","tid":597146,"uid":27568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:09:21.000Z","msg":"自我增值<br />\n自學成材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:14:25.000Z","msg":"技術人才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}